Description: Base class for all DL Backing beans. //FIXME - class name is misleading The main role of this class is to get the current DL process context. This class uses getCurrentProcessContext method of BasePage 

        public ProcessContext getCurrentProcessContext() {
                return ((SessionContext) this.getSessionScope().get(
                                PROCESS_CONTEXT_SESSION_KEY)).getCurrentProcessContext();
        }
